  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=52b20010&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FBMIuxTte9jIfY47ZXraNIeTjSXicLMmOTtNyjo9DVYuKcQqotmHcUQxiaWdLDZWzjV8yicq6P9bnVtvAcuT0rfibnQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:2.5px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">来源</span></strong></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Source</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 2px;border-color: rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 8px 11px 0px;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">标题：&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 硬件创业，我踩过的那些坑，这次全都告诉你！</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">分享者：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">王乐FOLOTOy 创始人</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/68d53d90cdf6fc18f3de8689\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.xiaoyuzhoufm.com/episode/68d53d90cdf6fc18f3de8689</a></span></span></span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img width=\"100%\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5648148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0744f3bc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FBMIuxTte9jIfY47ZXraNIeTjSXicLMmOTdvgkUBDeQOdic5ic6dbcvmhBibQzh96skOXP5F3gClqicgVU4hm7ELxVmA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">要点</span></b></span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></b><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Key Takeaways</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI玩具爆发，一个新行业诞生</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">创业从爆改家里的旧玩具开始</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">最早的用户是“想偷懒的爸爸”</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">瞄准千万台存量市场做“换脑”</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">诡异向日葵：选品看TikTok热度</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">最大的坑是帮用户“配网”</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">开端：两个“想偷懒的爸爸”</span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img width=\"100%\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=13c79a32&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIfY47ZXraNIeTjSXicLMmOTcdYobXUHib6CgBJ5uLm2TQCIibHXDay04l3xbjCj8Nm4DhYxO0ib39agA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">任鑫：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我回到办公室看到桌上有个向日葵……一边说话一边扭啊扭啊扭，各种婀娜各种鬼畜。我当时就觉得受到了精神污染。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">任鑫：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">后来参加活动，桌上放了个巨大的熊猫……我摸了一个像那个熊猫的头，然后就觉得巨好摸……这个质感怎么这么好。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我是一个爸爸，然后我的那个搭档他也是一个爸爸。我们觉得这个东西（大模型）还挺有价值的，希望能够让小朋友们也能够通过他们合适的方式去用。</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">播客主持人任鑫分享了他第一次接触 folotoy 产品的经历：</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个是让他“一辈子都记得”的、扭动极其“妖艳”和“诡异”的向日葵，他直言“受到了精神污染”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。另一个则是一个手感“巨好摸”的熊猫，好摸到他“全程抱在怀里摸他的头”，显得非常不专业。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两个产品都来自王乐的公司。王乐介绍，创业的初衷非常简单：他和搭档都是爸爸，自己经常玩 ChatGPT，觉得这东西很有价值，希望孩子也能用上。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">更直接的一个想法是，有了这个 AI 玩具陪娃，“我就不用费口舌了，我坐旁边看着，跟着他一起玩就行了”。就像任鑫也会在孩子不停问问题时，把手机丢给他跟 ChatGPT 聊。</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种“爸爸都有的偷懒想法”，成了 AI 玩具最早的起点</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">验证：从爆改“火火兔”开始</span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img width=\"100%\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4df4190c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIfY47ZXraNIeTjSXicLMmOT8BWx1tPd16Eic9meGdobsjdNbJmia2ht9pUfxpibEicLLxwO9emmCIms8g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我女儿比较小，她就玩那个火火兔。我当时就看到，我就觉得……那我把 GPT 给装进去，那是不是他就自己可以去让生成故事。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我那个同事也非常厉害，然后就鼓捣自己画板子，搞个模块一整，就几天他把 demo 就搭出来了。</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">最早的 MVP (Minimum Viable Product，最小可行产品) 诞生于一次偶然。王乐看到女儿在玩“火火兔”故事机，他立刻想到：“我把 GPT 装进去，它不就能自己讲故事、回答问题了吗？”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">他把这个想法告诉了搭档（也是一位爸爸），搭档也说“我也需要”。他的搭档动手能力极强，自己画板子、搞模块，几天之内就把一个 Demo 搭了出来。他们把这个模块塞进了旧的火火兔，发现效果“蛮好的”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐本身是开发者，活跃于推特。他把这个“爆改”的想法和 Demo 分享到推特上，没想到反响“特别的好”。很多中文圈的大佬、大V 都来联系他，他们都是“Daddy”，都说“我也需要这个东西”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这让他们意识到一个巨大的机会。他们调研后发现，像火火兔、米兔（小米的产品）这类故事机，在市场上的“保有量非常的高”，预估至少有上千万台的存量。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">于是，他们做出了一个关键决策：</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">先不开模具做新玩具，而是针对这几款保有量最大的产品，只做“里面的主板”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。他们录了教学视频，教爸爸们怎么拆开玩具螺丝，把原来的主板换成他们带大模型的板子——本质上是给玩具“换脑子”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个“换脑”方案大受欢迎，甚至导致闲鱼和拼多多上的“二手火火兔都被搞涨价了”。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 0px 10px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">爆款</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“精神污染”的向日葵是怎么选出来的？</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img width=\"100%\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2546296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=11750e15&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIfY47ZXraNIeTjSXicLMmOTiaSXuibA9xjBjRJGIlnaP0DSL0WoGl5zGH0IBrobtH9csSlCicsqa7SFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">任鑫：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">你们试出来向日葵是一个好的路径，是怎么试出来的？</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们去看了一下就会发现就是像仙人掌之类的玩具，它的传播的效果特别的好。一看就是有大量的相关的这种视频，让人印象很深刻。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">另外就是说我们也会去看一些电商的这个销量……有一家店可能这类型的玩具它一年就能卖10万台或者100万台。我认为这个事情市场肯定是确定性的。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">任鑫：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我觉得你们很聪明。先看 tiktok 上哪一类的内容会火……再看说哪一类玩具它本来就卖的比较好……我再往往上面凑。</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在卖替换主板的同时，他们也收到了各种各样的需求，比如仙人掌、电话机、毛绒玩具等。那么，到底该选择做什么形态的产品呢？“向日葵”这样的爆款是怎么诞生的？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐分享了他们的数据驱动选品法，核心有两步：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一，看传播性。他们去扒抖音和 TikTok，找出那些播放量上亿的玩具视频。他们发现，像“仙人掌”这类玩具，“传播的效果特别的好”，视频让人印象深刻。</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">这保证了产品未来做营销时，可以“生成一些很特别的这种视频”，自带传播效应。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二，看确定性。他们去扒亚马逊等电商平台，看销量数据。如果发现某类玩具，在没有 AI 的情况下，一年都能卖 10 万台甚至 100 万台，王乐就认为“这个事情市场肯定是确定性的”，这东西肯定能卖掉。</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如主持人任鑫总结的：</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">先看什么火的概率大（传播性），再看什么可卖的概率大（市场存量），最后再把 AI 加上去，而不是闭门造车。</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">4</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">迭代：为什么必须做“一体机”？</span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img width=\"100%\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c00736be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIfY47ZXraNIeTjSXicLMmOT8dJSe4SSxLLJKfVlupdnTQ3riabhB5v2NO4sCzic1yWXnGpCHHecBjzg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们最早的时候也是讲一下，我是不是可以做一些什么挂件、底座……但是你做这个用户的这个反馈和观察来看，他其实整个的大家对于这个形态就不是特别的调度不高。他就觉得这个东西是有点割裂。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们现在的所有的产品它有一个很很明显的特点，它都是那种一体的……我无论如何会把这个硬件的部分塞到毛绒玩具里面。</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在确定了产品形态后，团队进行了大量的尝试。王乐坦言，市面上几乎所有的 AI 玩具形态，他们早期全部试过，包括做成挂件、底座等各种形式。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">但用户的反馈和观察显示，这些形态“有点割裂”。因此，他们现在所有的产品都有一个明显特点：一体化。他们会“无论如何会把这个硬件的部分塞到毛绒玩具里面”，做成拆不下来的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐认为，</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这关乎保护孩子的“想象力”。如果一个东西可以被拆卸、装到别处，孩子就会意识到“这东西就是假的”，想象力就被破坏了</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。AI 玩具应该是一个“超拟人”的整体，就像动画片里的角色变成了现实。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">5</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">踩坑：最大的敌人是“配网”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img width=\"100%\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2583333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=84399213&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIfY47ZXraNIeTjSXicLMmOTpMlkeb95dB5RZIsfyicYsNrOjr0vXB8YB9PScUt6d5bXKkMiaOC694qg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">收到的最多的批评是什么？……（比如）你这个配网很麻烦，要按键，然后那个反应又慢。</span></span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们把国内的几乎所有型号的安卓手机都搞了一台去测试一下。他的这个手机底下应该是怎么来配网，我们都录了视频。</span></span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们后面把4G也给做上……就进一步的去思考，降低用户上手的这样一个过程。</span></span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们马上就会推出一款……可能是这个价位（300到500）里面……全球的第一款同时支持2.4G和5G的一个量产的这样的一个产品。</span></span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当被问及收到最多的批评时，王乐毫不犹豫地指向了</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">产品层面的问题，尤其是“配网”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为最早的产品是“给 Daddy（开发者）做的”，团队没太考虑普通用户的上手问题，搞得“比较复杂，都很硬核”。当产品破圈后，复杂的配网流程（按键、反应慢）成了最大的槽点。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了解决这个痛点，他们花了巨大的精力：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">软件优化：</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;团队买来了“国内几乎所有型号的安卓手机”，一台一台测试，录制了所有机型的配网教学视频。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">硬件升级（4G）：</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;为了彻底解决 Wi-Fi 配网的麻烦，他们后续的产品直接内置了 4G SIM 卡，极大降低了上手门槛。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">硬件升级（5G）：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;针对家庭 Wi-Fi 2.4G 频段拥挤、语音丢包影响体验的问题，他们即将推出全球首款在 300-500 元价位同时支持 2.4G 和 5G Wi-Fi 的产品。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">6</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 0px 10px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">破圈</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从“To Daddy”到“To Mommy”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img width=\"100%\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=abb9daf9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIfY47ZXraNIeTjSXicLMmOT7ed8UX2yTDCXE93o87iaDvgwrqCqJHR7BWmVAicHoje2p4gYR1hG6OjA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们是给 daddy 做玩具。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们上了天猫之后，国内慢慢的就会从我们从这个 to daddy 的就变成一个 to妈咪的产品了。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">就会不仅仅是这个玩的部分，它又体现了寓教于乐。就是玩和学我们都在体现。我们一直讲叫寓教于乐。三分学七分玩。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们在六一的时候跟招商银行去合作的，就是主打小朋友财商教育的。</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Follow toy 的早期用户画像非常清晰：开发者和极客爸爸，即“To Daddy”。但当他们去年底上了天猫等主流电商平台后，用户画像发生了根本性转变，变成了“To Mommy”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个转变直接影响了产品的定位。妈妈们购买时，不仅仅是希望它“好玩”，更希望它能“学习”，产品必须体现“寓教于乐”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，团队开始强化产品的教育属性，定位为“三分学七分玩”。他们开始切入更深的场景，比如与博物馆 IP 合作、与招商银行合作推出“财商教育”的限量款玩具。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">7</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">壁垒</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">硬件100%自研，如何搞定供应链？</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img width=\"100%\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c765b038&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIfY47ZXraNIeTjSXicLMmOTe0FjoIYGL6mMDzXWHVyr5rytLybFC0vZ5kU7hic3k0wJjc2CR1Ac7Rw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们到目前为止都没有用过方案，解决方案都是我们自己做的。</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">王乐：</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们就真的去深入到那个地方（东莞、扬州）……看他的那个标签是哪家厂子做的，然后就跑到他们，跟他们老板联系。</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当产品入局者变多，核心竞争力在哪里？王乐的答案是：100% 自研硬件。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们没有选择深圳大量的“解决方案商”。王乐解释了原因：第一，方案商会把同一套方案卖给 A、B、C，导致“所有东西都是做一样的了”，产品没有差异化。第二，无法控制迭代速度，而 folotoy 希望能像软件一样快速迭代硬件。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么，一个 20 多人的小团队，如何搞定复杂的硬件和毛绒玩具供应链？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于硬件，他们选择直接对接“芯片原厂”，如乐鑫，从源头自研。对于毛绒玩具，他们采取了最“笨”的办法：深入产业聚集地（如东莞、扬州），在市场上看哪个玩具做得好，然后翻看标签，找到是哪家工厂做的，再直接“跑过去跟他们老板联系”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了让这些大厂（甚至是上市公司）愿意接单，他们展现了足够的诚意，比如直接下了 1 万台的订单。王乐强调，在用料上“不省钱”，比如一个毛绒的成本就要六七十块，以此来建立品质壁垒。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Closing Thoughts</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多好玩的产品，都不是事前规划出来的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一开始王乐只是爆改了火火兔，验证了市场真需求之后才开始动作。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">而真的打市场时，也不是傲慢的教育市场，而是看什么视频在短视频里能火、什么玩具形态本来在电商就好卖，然后再决定的产品形态。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后在聊到具体产品落地时，谈的也是很具体的“怎么把玩具顺利联网”这种朴素的痛点。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">很喜欢这种真诚朴素的分享啊。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "folotoy 创始人王乐分享了 AI 玩具创业从“爆改”旧玩具到一体化产品、解决用户痛点、构建供应链壁垒的实践经验。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "folotoy 创始人王乐分享了 AI 玩具创业从“爆改”旧玩具到一体化产品、解决用户痛点、构建供应链壁垒的实践经验。",
  "summary": "文章通过对 folotoy 创始人王乐的访谈，深入探讨了 AI 玩具领域的创业历程和关键策略。王乐从“偷懒的爸爸”这一用户洞察出发，通过“爆改”旧故事机，以“换脑”形式验证了 AI 玩具的市场需求。随后，他介绍了数据驱动的选品方法，结合 TikTok 传播性和电商销量，成功打造出爆款产品。文章还详细阐述了产品从“To Daddy”到“To Mommy”的用户画像转变，以及产品定位从“好玩”转向“寓教于乐”的关键策略调整。此外，还介绍了如何通过硬件一体化设计和解决“配网”等用户痛点来提升产品体验。最后，王乐分享了通过 100% 自研硬件和深入供应链来构建竞争壁垒的经验，为 AI 硬件创业者提供了宝贵的实践指导。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 玩具创业可从“爆改”现有产品验证市场需求，通过“偷懒的爸爸”洞察找到早期用户。",
      "explanation": "folotoy 团队将 GPT 集成到旧故事机中，满足了家长“偷懒陪娃”的需求，通过低成本 MVP 快速验证了 AI 玩具的市场潜力，并成功吸引了早期开发者用户。"
    },
    {
      "point": "数据驱动是爆款选品的关键，需结合社交媒体传播性与电商市场存量。",
      "explanation": "folotoy 通过分析 TikTok 上的病毒视频和电商平台的销量数据，识别出具有高传播潜力和确定性市场需求的玩具品类，避免闭门造车，确保产品能迅速被市场接受。"
    },
    {
      "point": "产品形态应追求一体化设计，以保护用户（儿童）的想象力，避免割裂感。",
      "explanation": "团队尝试多种产品形态后发现，一体化的设计能让 AI 玩具更像动画角色真实存在，防止拆卸带来的“虚假感”，从而更好地维护儿童的沉浸式体验和想象空间。"
    },
